{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id798d5282-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1632"},"text":"§ 1632.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Form of disclosure; additional information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id798d5283-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Information clearly and conspicuously disclosed; “annual percentage rate” and “finance charge”; order of disclosures and use of different terminology","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Information required by this subchapter shall be disclosed clearly and conspicuously, in accordance with regulations of the Bureau. The terms “annual percentage rate” and “finance charge” shall be disclosed more conspicuously than other terms, data, or information provided in connection with a transaction, except information relating to the identify of the creditor. Except as provided in subsection (c), regulations of the Bureau need not require that disclosures pursuant to this subchapter be made in the order set forth in this subchapter and, except as otherwise provided, may permit the use of terminology different from that employed in this subchapter if it conveys substantially the same meaning.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id798d5284-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Optional information by creditor or lessor","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any creditor or lessor may supply additional information or explanation with any disclosures required under parts D and E and, except as provided in sections 1637a(b)(3) and 1638(b)(1) of this title, under this part.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id798d5285-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Tabular format required for certain disclosures under section 1637(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5286-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The information described in paragraphs (1)(A), (3)(B)(i)(I), (4)(A), and (4)(C)(i)(I) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637/c"},"text":"section 1637(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall be—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5287-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" disclosed in the form and manner which the Bureau shall prescribe by regulations; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5288-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" placed in a conspicuous and prominent location on or with any written application, solicitation, or other document or paper with respect to which such disclosure is required.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5289-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Tabular format","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d528a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Form of table to be prescribed","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In the regulations prescribed under paragraph (1)(A) of this subsection, the Bureau shall require that the disclosure of such information shall, to the extent the Bureau determines to be practicable and appropriate, be in the form of a table which—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id798d528b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" contains clear and concise headings for each item of such information; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id798d528c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provides a clear and concise form for stating each item of information required to be disclosed under each such heading.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d528d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Bureau discretion in prescribing order and wording of table","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In prescribing the form of the table under subparagraph (A), the Bureau may—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id798d528e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" list the items required to be included in the table in a different order than the order in which such items are set forth in paragraph (1)(A) or (4)(A) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637/c"},"text":"section 1637(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id798d528f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" subject to subparagraph (C), employ terminology which is different than the terminology which is employed in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637/c"},"text":"section 1637(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" if such terminology conveys substantially the same meaning."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5290-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/c/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Grace period","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Either the heading or the statement under the heading which relates to the time period referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637/c/1/A/iii"},"text":"section 1637(c)(1)(A)(iii) of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall contain the term “grace period”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id798d5291-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional electronic disclosures","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5292-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Posting agreements","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Each creditor shall establish and maintain an Internet site on which the creditor shall post the written agreement between the creditor and the consumer for each credit card account under an open-end consumer credit plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5293-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Creditor to provide contracts to the Bureau","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Each creditor shall provide to the Bureau, in electronic format, the consumer credit card agreements that it publishes on its Internet site.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5294-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Record repository","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Bureau shall establish and maintain on its publicly available Internet site a central repository of the consumer credit card agreements received from creditors pursuant to this subsection, and such agreements shall be easily accessible and retrievable by the public.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5295-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exception","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subsection shall not apply to individually negotiated changes to contractual terms, such as individually modified workouts or renegotiations of amounts owed by a consumer under an open end consumer credit plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id798d5296-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s1632/d/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Bureau, in consultation with the other Federal banking agencies (as that term is defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1681a"},"text":"section 1681a of this title","children":[],"tail":") and the Bureau,"},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002337"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002337"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original."}],"tail":" may promulgate regulations to implement this subsection, including specifying the format for posting the agreements on the Internet sites of creditors and establishing exceptions to paragraphs (1) and (2), in any case in which the administrative burden outweighs the benefit of increased transparency, such as where a credit card plan has a de minimis number of consumer account holders."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id798d5297-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/321/tI/s122"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–321, title I, § 122","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-05-29"},"text":"May 29, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/152"},"text":"82 Stat. 152","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/495/tIII/s307/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–495, title III, § 307(e)","children":[],"tail":", (f), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1516"},"text":"88 Stat. 1516","children":[],"tail":", 1517; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/221/tVI/s611"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–221, title VI, § 611","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-03-31"},"text":"Mar. 31, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/175"},"text":"94 Stat. 175","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/583/s2/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–583, § 2(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-03"},"text":"Nov. 3, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2966"},"text":"102 Stat. 2966","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/709/s2/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–709, § 2(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-23"},"text":"Nov. 23, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/4731"},"text":"102 Stat. 4731","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/24/tII/s204"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–24, title II, § 204","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/1746"},"text":"123 Stat. 1746","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/tX/s1100A/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, title X, § 1100A(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-07-21"},"text":"July 21, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/2107"},"text":"124 Stat. 2107","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id798d5298-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id798d5299-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id798d529a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—Subsecs. (a), (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100A/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100A(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Bureau” for “Board” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(2), (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100A/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100A(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Bureau” for “Board” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":" substituted “The Bureau, in” for “The Board, in” and “and the Bureau, may” for “and the Federal Trade Commission, may”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2009—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/24"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–24","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/583/s2/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–583, § 2(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Except as provided in subsection (c), regulations” for “Regulations”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/709"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–709","children":[],"tail":" substituted “sections 1637a(b)(3) and 1638(b)(1)” for “section 1638(b)(1)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/583/s2/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–583, § 2(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1980—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/221"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–221","children":[],"tail":" substituted provisions setting forth form of disclosure to meet requirements of this subchapter, for provisions setting forth form of disclosure authorized under this part or part D of this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/221"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–221","children":[],"tail":" substituted provisions setting forth disclosure requirements for additional information by creditors or lessors, for provisions setting forth disclosure requirements for additional information by creditors."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1974—Subsecs. (a), (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/495"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–495","children":[],"tail":" inserted references to part D of this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id798d529b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id798d529c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2010 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":" effective on the designated transfer date, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100H"},"text":"section 1100H of Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s552a"},"text":"section 552a of Title 5","children":[],"tail":", Government Organization and Employees."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id798d529d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2009 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/24"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–24","children":[],"tail":" effective 9 months after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2009","children":[],"tail":", except as otherwise specifically provided, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/24/s3"},"text":"section 3 of Pub. L. 111–24","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1602"},"text":"section 1602 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id798d529e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1988 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For effective date of amendments by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/709"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–709","children":[],"tail":", see Regulations; Effective Date note below."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id798d529f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1980 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/221"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–221","children":[],"tail":" effective on expiration of two years and six months after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-03-31"},"text":"Mar. 31, 1980","children":[],"tail":", with all regulations, forms, and clauses required to be prescribed to be promulgated at least one year prior to such effective date, and allowing any creditor to comply with any amendments, in accordance with the regulations, forms, and clauses prescribed by the Board prior to such effective date, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/221/s625"},"text":"section 625 of Pub. L. 96–221","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1602"},"text":"section 1602 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id798d52a0-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1974 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For effective date of amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/495"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–495","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/495/s308"},"text":"section 308 of Pub. L. 93–495","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1666"},"text":"section 1666 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id798d52a1-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Regulations; Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For provisions relating to promulgation of regulations to implement amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/709"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–709","children":[],"tail":", and effective date of such amendment in connection with those regulations, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/709/s7"},"text":"section 7 of Pub. L. 100–709","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637a"},"text":"section 1637a of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For provisions relating to promulgation of regulations to implement amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/583"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–583","children":[],"tail":", and effective date of such amendment in connection with those regulations, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/583/s7"},"text":"section 7 of Pub. L. 100–583","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1637"},"text":"section 1637 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
